FBIS3-15094 "drsov042_s_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-042 Document Type:Daily Report 3 Mar 1994 Georgia Russian Ministry To Control Actions in Georgia LD0203172694 Tbilisi IBERIA in Georgian 1530 GMT 2 Mar 94 LD0203172694 Tbilisi IBERIA Language: Georgian Article Type:BFN [Text] Tbilisi, 2 Mar -- According to IBERIA NEWS AGENCY a process of reorganization has been started at the Georgian Defense Ministry. The number of forces will gradually be cut and some structures abolished. All military actions will be controlled by the Russian Defense Ministry and, in particular, the command of the Russian military units deployed in the Transcaucasus.
